title: Ayeza Khan and Danish Taimur’s bathroom photos go viral
text:
(24 News) Pakistani actress Ayeza Khan’s bathroom photos with her husband Danish Taimur have gone viral on social media, which have angered her fans.
According to details, Pakistani actress Ayeza Khan has made her fans crazy by doing a photo shoot with her husband actor Danish Taimur in the bathroom. Hai and both are posing facing the camera, in the picture Ayeza Khan is seen wearing a monochrome gown while Danish Taimur is wearing a white vest with trousers.
In the picture, Ayeza Khan is sitting in the bathtub while Danish Taimur is sitting on the mandir of the bathtub, whose arm is being held by Ayeza Khan. Fed up, one Instagram user wrote, ‘Sister, you didn’t find any other place, you only found this bathtub for a photo shoot?’ Another angry user wrote, ‘People don’t even leave the bathroom for fame’.
Another Instagram user wrote that ‘Sister Esi Bhi Kya Nabhi Hi’, while another user wrote that ‘Dressing sense is not there and these madams are number one in spreading indecency’, remember that Danish Taimur and Ayeza Khan are deeply Married with fanfare on August 8, 2014 after an expression of friendship and love. The love-married couple has a daughter, Hareen, and a son, Ryan, with whom the two continue to share rich photos and videos.
Both are at the peak of their careers and have hit dramas back to back with great acting. Recently, the duo was seen spending a memorable day with the kids in the UK and shared pictures with their fans, who were all in awe. Liked the limit.
